{"repository": {"pullRequest": {"number": 1786, "title": "WIP: non-blocking show using trame/vtk", "body": "Closes #1784 (?)\r\n\r\nAPI:\r\n```python\r\nfrom cadquery.fig import Figure\r\nfrom cadquery.func import sphere, torus\r\n\r\n# this starts a server and opens a browser tab\r\nfig = Figure()\r\n\r\n# we can use show, the API is fluent\r\nfig.show(torus(10, 2), color='violet').show(sphere(5))\r\n\r\n# zoom to fit\r\nfig.fit()\r\n\r\n# clear\r\nfig.clear()\r\n```\r\n\r\n![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/0fb7a6d2-0c4e-4df2-95c7-c3daad9cc528)\r\n", "baseRefName": "master", "baseRefOid": "f07e7e0428d07140f3d9fea1c1c51c745f08f2db", "baseRepository": {"nameWithOwner": "CadQuery/cadquery"}, "url": "https://github.com/CadQuery/cadquery/pull/1786", "createdAt": "2025-03-10T07:11:04Z", "mergedAt": "2025-07-30T17:04:21Z"}}, "base": {"repo": {"full_name": "CadQuery/cadquery"}, "sha": "f07e7e0428d07140f3d9fea1c1c51c745f08f2db"}, "diff_url": "https://github.com/CadQuery/cadquery/pull/1786.diff", "number": 1786, "created_at": "2025-03-10T07:11:04Z", "merged_at": "2025-07-30T17:04:21Z", "resolved_issues": [1784]}
{"repository": {"pullRequest": {"number": 1808, "title": "Local and non-manifold sewing", "body": "Supports advanced use cases of building shapes from individual faces.\r\n\r\n- [x] local and non-manifold sewing\r\n- [x] history for `shell` and `solid`\r\n- [x] `addHole` for `Face`\r\n- [x] tests\r\n- [x] project (normal projection)\r\n- [x] docs\r\n\r\n```python\r\nfrom cadquery.func import *\r\nfrom cadquery.vis import show\r\n\r\n# box\r\nb = box(1,1,1)\r\n# bottom face\r\nbb = b.faces('<Z')\r\n# top faces\r\nbt = b.faces('>Z')\r\n\r\n# make inner tube \r\nc = circle(0.45)\r\ncf = extrude(c, (0,0,1))\r\n\r\n# add holes to the bottom and top face\r\nbb_hole = bb.addHole(c)\r\nbt_hole = bt.addHole(cf.edges('>Z'))\r\n\r\nhist = {}\r\n\r\n# construct the final solid\r\nrs = solid(\r\n    (b.remove(bt, bb).faces(), #side faces\r\n     bb_hole, # bottom with a hole\r\n     cf, # inner cylinder face\r\n     bt_hole, # top with a hole\r\n    ),\r\n    history=hist,\r\n)\r\n\r\nshow(rs)\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/7901d35c-0771-4250-978f-1116d0ee89a1)\r\n", "baseRefName": "master", "baseRefOid": "8c68faad4761df9e0eb9ab042346ef53c598b617", "baseRepository": {"nameWithOwner": "CadQuery/cadquery"}, "url": "https://github.com/CadQuery/cadquery/pull/1808", "createdAt": "2025-04-13T10:01:58Z", "mergedAt": "2025-05-04T19:05:31Z"}}, "base": {"repo": {"full_name": "CadQuery/cadquery"}, "sha": "8c68faad4761df9e0eb9ab042346ef53c598b617"}, "diff_url": "https://github.com/CadQuery/cadquery/pull/1808.diff", "number": 1808, "created_at": "2025-04-13T10:01:58Z", "merged_at": "2025-05-04T19:05:31Z", "resolved_issues": [1800]}
